\c 32
\s Mhuru yegoridhe
\p
\v 1 Zvino vanhu vaona kuti Mozisi unononoka kuburuka kubva mugomo\x + 24.18. Det. 9.9.\x*, vanhu vakazviunganidza kuna Aroni ndokuti kwaari: Simuka, tiitire vamwari\x + Mab. 7.40.\x* vanotitungamirira\x + 13.21.\x*, nokuti Mozisi uyu, murume wakatikwidza kubva munyika yeEgipita, hatizivi chaitika kwaari.
\v 2 Zvino Aroni wakati kwavari: Kwaturai zvindori zvegoridhe zviri\x + Vato. 8.24-27.\x* panzeve dzevakadzi venyu \add ne\add*dzevanakomana venyu nedzevanasikana venyu, muunze kwandiri.
\v 3 Zvino vanhu vose vakakwatura zvindori zvegoridhe zvaiva panzeve dzavo, vakauisa kuna Aroni.
\v 4 Iye ndokugamuchira paruoko\x + 32.8. Det. 9.16. Neh. 9.18. Map. 106.19. Mab. 7.41. Vato. 17.3,4. 1 Madz. 12.28.\x* rwavo, akazviumba nemudziyo wekuveza, akazviita mhuru yakaumbwa nekunyungudusa. Ivo ndokuti: Ndivo vamwari vako, Israeri, vakakukwidza kubva munyika yeEgipita\x + 32.8. Det. 9.16. Neh. 9.18. Map. 106.19. Mab. 7.41. Vato. 17.3,4. 1 Madz. 12.28.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino Aroni aona wakavaka aritari pamberi payo; Aroni ndokudanidzira ndokuti: Mangwana kuchava nemutambo kuna Jehovha\x + Rev. 23.2,4,21,37. 2 Madz. 10.20.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino vakamuka mangwanani-ngwanani ndokupa zvipo zvinopiswa, vakauyawo nezvipo zvekuyananisa, vanhu ndokugara pasi kudya nekunwa\x + 1 VaKori. 10.7.\x*, ndokusimuka kutamba\x + Gen.. 26.8. 39.14,17.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Enda, buruka, nokuti vaora vanhu vako vawakakwidza kubva munyika\x + Det. 9.8,12.\x* yeEgipita\x + Gen.. 6.11,12. Det. 4.16. 32.5. Vato. 2.19. Hos. 9.9.\x*.
\v 8 Vatsauka nekukurumidza kubva panzira yandakavaraira\x + 20.3,4,23. Det. 9.16.\x*, vakazviitira mhuru yakaumbwa nekunyungudusa ndokuinamata uye vakaibaira ndokuti: Ava ndivamwari vako, Israeri, vakakukwidza kubva munyika yeEgipita\x + 32.4.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Ndaona vanhu ava, zvino tarira, vanhu vemitsipa mikukutu\x + 33.3,5. 34.9. Det. 9.6,13. 31.27. 2 Makor. 30.8. Mab. 7.51. Isa. 48.4.\x*.
\v 10 Zvinowo ndirege hako\x + Det. 9.14.\x*, kuti hasha dzangu dzivapfutire, kuti ndivapedze\x + 22.24.\x*; asi iwe ndichakuita uve rudzi rukuru\x + Num.. 14.12.\x*.
\v 11 Asi Mozisi wakanyengetedza chiso chaJehovha Mwari wake ndokuti\x + Det. 9.18,26-29. Map. 74.1,2. 106.23.\x*: Sei, Jehovha, hasha dzenyu dzichipfutira vanhu venyu, vamakabudisa munyika yeEgipita nesimba guru uye neruoko rune simba?
\v 12 VaEgipita vachataura sei vachiti: Wakavabudisira chakaipa, kuvauraira mumakomo, nekuvapedza kubva pachiso chenyika\x + Num.. 14.13. Det. 32.27.\x*? Dzokai pahasha dzinotyisa, muzvidembe pachakaipa chinorwisa vanhu venyu\x + 32.14. Gen.. 6.6.\x*.
\v 13 Rangarirai Abhurahama, Isaka, naIsraeri, varanda venyu, kwamakazvipikira kwavari\x + Gen.. 22.16. VaHeb. 6.13.\x*, ndokuti kwavari: Ndichawanza mbeu yenyu senyeredzi\x + Gen.. 12.7. 13.15. 15.7,18. 26.4. 28.13. 35.11,12. 48.16.\x* dzematenga, nenyika yose iyi, sezvandakareva, ndichaipa kumbeu yenyu, uye vachagara nhaka rinhi narinhi.
\v 14 Zvino Jehovha akazvidemba pachakaipa chaaiva ati achaitira vanhu vake\x + 32.12. Map. 106.45. 1 Makor. 21.15. Jer. 18.8. 26.13,19. Jona 3.10. 4.2.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Zvino Mozisi wakatendeuka ndokuburuka kubva\x + Det. 9.15.\x* mugomo, nemahwendefa maviri echipupuriro muruoko rwake; mahwendefa akanyorwa nhivi dzawo dzose; akanyorwa seri neseri.
\v 16 Zvino mahwendefa aiva basa raMwari, nerunyoro rwaiva rwuri runyoro rwaMwari, rwakafomborwa pamahwendefa\x + 31.18.\x*.
\v 17 Joshua wakati anzwa\x + 17.9. 24.13. 33.11.\x* mhere-mhere yevanhu vanopururudza, wakati kuna Mozisi: Kune mhere-mhere yehondo kumusasa.
\v 18 Iye ndokuti: Haisi mhere-mhere yekudanidzira kwekukunda, uye haisi mhere-mhere yekudanidzira kwekukundwa; ndinonzwa mhere-mhere yekuimba\x + Jer. 51.14.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Zvino zvakaitika paakangoswedera pamusasa, kuti wakaona mhuru\x + Det. 9.16,17,21.\x* nekutamba; hasha dzaMozisi ndokupfuta, ndokukanda mahwendefa kubva mumaoko ake, ndokuaputsa mujinga megomo.
\v 20 Zvino wakatora mhuru yavaiva vaita, akapisa mumoto, aka\add i\add*kuya kuita upfu, akaikusha pamusoro pemvura, ndokunwisa vana vaIsraeri.
\v 21 Mozisi ndokuti kuna Aroni: Vanhu ava vakuitirei kusvika wauisira chivi ichi chikuru\x + Gen.. 20.9.\x*?
\v 22 Aroni ndokuti: Hasha dzashe wangu ngadzirege kupfuta; imwi munoziva vanhu, kuti \add vakarerekera\add* kukutadza\x + 14.11. 15.24. 16.2,20. 17.2,4.\x*.
\v 23 Nokuti vakati kwandiri: Tiitirei vamwari vachatitungamirira, nokuti Mozisi uyu, murume wakatikwidza kubva munyika yeEgipita, hatizivi chaitika kwaari\x + 32.1.\x*.
\v 24 Zvino ndakati kwavari: Ani nani ane goridhe ngavarikwature\x + 32.2-4.\x*; zvino vakandipa; ini ndokurikandira mumoto, ndokubuda mhuru iyi.
\p
\v 25 Zvino Mozisi wakati aona kuti vanhu vasunungurwa, nokuti Aroni waiva avasunungura kuti vasekwe nevavengi vavo\x + 2 Makor. 28.19.\x*,
\v 26 Mozisi wakanomira musuwo remusasa, ndokuti: Ani nani ari waJehovha, \add ngaauye\add* kwandiri. Vana vaRevhi vose vakaungana kwaari.
\v 27 Zvino wakati kwavari: Anoreva seizvi Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri: Umwe neumwe ngaaise munondo wake pachidya chake, mufambe-fambe muchibva pane rimwe suwo muchienda kune rimwe suwo pakati pemusasa; umwe neumwe auraye hama yake, neumwe neumwe shamwari yake, neumwe neumwe munhu wekwake\x + Num.. 25.5. Det. 33.9.\x*.
\v 28 Vana vaRevhi vakaita maererano neshoko raMozisi; nemusi iwowo vakawa vanenge vane zvuru zvitatu kubva pavanhu.
\v 29 Zvino Mozisi wakati: Zviparadzanisei nhasi kuna Jehovha, kuti munhu umwe neumwe arwe nemwanakomana wake uye nehama yake; kuti ape ropafadzo pamusoro pako nhasi\x + Num.. 25.11,12,13. Det. 13.6-11. Zek. 13.3. Mat. 10.37.\x*.
\p
\v 30 Zvino zvakaitika mangwana, kuti Mozisi wakati kuvanhu: Imwi makatadza \add ne\add*kutadza\x + 32.21,32. 1 Zvak. 12.20.\x* kukuru, asi zvino ndichakwira kuna Jehovha, zvimwe\x + 2 Zvak. 16.12. Amo. 5.15.\x* ndichaitira kutadza kwenyu chiyananiso\x + Num.. 25.13.\x*.
\v 31 Mozisi akadzokera kuna Jehovha, ndokuti\x + Det. 9.18.\x*: Haiwa, vanhu ava vakatadza \add ne\add*kutadza kukuru, vakazviitira vamwari vegoridhe\x + 20.23.\x*.
\v 32 Zvino dai muchivakanganwira henyu kutadza kwavo; asi kana zvisina \add kudaro\add*\x + Gen.. 30.27.\x*, ndidzimei henyu\x + VaRom. 9.3.\x* kubva pabhuku renyu ramakanyora\x + Map. 56.8. 69.28. 139.16. Dhan. 12.1. VaFir. 4.3. Zvak. 3.5. 13.8. 17.8. 20.12,15. 21.27.22.19.\x*.
\v 33 Jehovha ndokuti kuna Mozisi: Uyo wakanditadzira, ndiye wandichadzima kubva pabhuku rangu\x + Eze. 18.4,20.\x*.
\v 34 Zvino chienda, uperekedze vanhu vaende kwandakakuudza; tarira, mutumwa wangu achakutungamirira, asi pazuva\x + 33.2,3. 14.19.\x* rekuranga kwangu, ndicharanga chivi chavo pamusoro pavo.
\v 35 Jehovha akarova vanhu, nokuti vaita mhuru iyo Aroni yaakaita.